  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Pharmaceutical Supply Chain watch</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">1. this will include the launching of the project with key stakeholders, to validate the existing data on the registration and re-registration of products and dissemination of the findings
2. Sensitization meeting and advocacy training for the members of the National Executive Council members to equip them with the planned action.
3. Create awareness of the impending action through the media: radios, televisions and newspapers and engage the relevant policy makers. 
4.Educate media houses on the advocacy plan action (Radio and Television)
5.To sensitize the public through Media(Radio and Television)</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">&#x2022; Downward revision in registration fees, with attendant increase in product registrations from greater compliance.
&#x2022; More pharmaceutical products registered for the safety of the patients.</narrative>
  </description>
